              "spans": [
                {
                  "bbox": [72, 80, 540, 180],
                  "type": "text",
                  "content": "Prior work on retrieval-augmented generation spans multiple research directions. DPR (Karpukhin et al., 2020) introduced dense passage retrieval using dual-encoder architectures. RAG (Lewis et al., 2020) combined retrieval with sequence-to-sequence generation. More recent work has focused on improving retrieval quality and generation faithfulness.",
                  "score": 0.97
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
