                  "bbox": [72, 430, 540, 520],
                  "type": "text",
                  "content": "Given the retrieved context C = {c_1, ..., c_k}, the generation model produces an answer conditioned on both the query and the retrieved passages. We employ a cross-attention mechanism to weight the retrieved context appropriately.",
