                  "bbox": [72, 80, 540, 180],
                  "type": "text",
                  "content": "We evaluate AdaptRAG on three standard QA benchmarks: NaturalQuestions (NQ), TriviaQA (TQA), and WebQuestions (WQ). Our experiments demonstrate the effectiveness of the adaptive retrieval strategy across different query types and difficulty levels.",
                  "score": 0.97
                }
